        "subject": "OSF-69 dne: add DNE architecture",
        "message": "OSF-69 dne: add DNE architecture\n\nThe patch is too big to be reviewed now, and it needs to be\nsplit. Land it just for some tests.\n\n1. Add DNE architecture based on LOD/OSP. OSP will be used\nto communicate between MDT and MDT. On the remote MDT, OUT\n(object update target) will be used to handle the object\nupdates between MDT, which talks to OSD directly.\n\n3. Some mgs llog fixes for DNE.\nChange-Id: If6be9dcaedb01e8fcd93a0d14389582a06673759\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
